quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,170,"Si ɓe wi'anaa:\"Jokkee kon ko Allah Jippini\", ɓe mbi'a:\"Ko woni, men njokkay ko men tawri kon baabiraaɓe amen\";e hay si baabiraaɓe maɓɓe ɓen haqqilataa hay e huunde ɓe haanditaaki"
  2,171,"Misal ɓen yedduɓe hino wa'i wa on ewnotooɗo kon ko nanataa si wanaa noddaandu e ewnal. Ko faaɗuɗi, mumiɗuɗi, wumuɗi; kaŋji ɗi haqqiltaa"
  2,172,"Ko onon yo ɓen gomɗimɓe! Ñamee immorde e laaɓuɗi ɗi Men Arsiki on, jaarnon Allah si on wonii ko Kaŋko rewoton"
  2,173,"Anndee ko O Harminani on, ko jiiɓe, e ƴiiƴam, e teewu kose, e [huunde hirsiraande] daginiraande ko woori Allah. Kala on duñaaɗo [e ñaamugol ɗum] hara wanaa ɓewɗo wanaa jaggituɗo, bakkatu fawaaki mo. Pellet Allah ko Ya'fotooɗo Yurmeteeɗo"
  2,174,"Pellet ɓen suuɗooɓe ko Allah Jippini kon e Deftere nden, hiɓe soodira ɗum cogguwel famɗungel. Ɓen ɗon alaa waɗude ka deedi maɓɓe si wanaa yiite ngen; Allah Yeewtidtaa ɓe ñalnde darngal, O Laɓɓiŋtaa ɓe, hino woodani ɓe lepte muusuɗe"
  2,175,"Ko ɓen ngoni soodirɓe majjere nden peewal, e lepte ɗen ya'fuyee. kaawse ko muññoriɓe ka yiite"
  2,176,"Ɗuum noon, ko fii Allah Jippinirii Deftere nden goonga. pellet ɓen luutondirɓe e Deftere nden ɓe ngonii e lurral woɗɗungal"